title: Ep 337 - Iyer Is Hurt
shortDesc: While trying to help Taarak get out of the society, Iyer gets stuck and falls on his leg. Seeing Iyer in so much pain, Sodhi carries him to home.

title: Ep 338 - Umpteenth Attempt To Move The Truck
shortDesc: Even after trying his best, even Sodhi is unable to move the truck away from the entrance. Later, he calls one of his friends who can come and tow the truck away using a towing machine.

title: Ep 339 - Mastermind Daya
shortDesc: While the doctor helplessly waits outside the society compound, Daya comes up with a great idea to get the doctor into the society. What is Daya's idea? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 340 - Truck Load Of Fake Weapons
shortDesc: Abdul finds out that there are big cartons of weapons in the truck.The members of Gokuldham society report to the police. Later they realize that the weapons are fake. But who parked the truck at the entrance? Will the driver get caught?

title: Ep 341 - Gokuldham Has A Robber
shortDesc: Taarak Mehta returns home to witness a man walking towards the terrace. He immediately informs Bhide and others to gather on the terrace to catch the robber. Will the robber get caught?

title: Ep 342 - Exam Preparations
shortDesc: While Taarak is showing his love for his wife, Tappu Sena is getting a basing from Bhide for not being serious about the approaching exams. How will Tappu Sena take the exam stress?

title: Ep 343 - Tappu Caught Red-Handed
shortDesc: Bhide tries to warn Jethalal about Tappu's carelessness towards exams. But, Jethalal shuts him off saying Tappu has been studying. But when they check, Bhide catches him reading a comic book. How will the Gadas react to this?

title: Ep 344 - The Parent Teachers Meeting
shortDesc: Tappu Sena is informed that there will be a parent-teachers' meeting. All the kids are worried about getting scoldings at the meeting, especially Tappu. What will he tell his father? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 345 - Champaklal Attends The Meeting
shortDesc: Champaklal decides to attend the meeting at Tappu's school. But, he says that if anyone speaks Tappu with disrespect, he will bash them. What will happen at the school? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 346 - Principal Is Angry At Tappu Sena
shortDesc: The parents take time to reach the school for the meeting which angers the principal. He warns the kids that if the parents don't arrive in 10 minutes, he won't allow the kids to write the exam. Will the parents arrive on time?

title: Ep 347 - Bhide Is Furious
shortDesc: To everyone's surprise, the reports turn out to be the opposite of everyone's expectations. Bhide scolds Sonu for getting a bad report. He compares Tappu's report and says that he is ashamed of himself for being too lenient.

title: Ep 348 - Diet Papads Ruined
shortDesc: While talking about Bhide's tension regarding Sonu's report, Taarak spills water on the special papads Anjali had ordered. How will Anjali react to it?

title: Ep 349 - Sonu Leaves The House
shortDesc: Distressed about getting scoldings from her father, Sonu decides to leave the house. Will she come back home? How will the society members help the Bhide family find their daughter?

title: Ep 350 - Taaraks Tricky Riddles
shortDesc: The society's men are all relaxing at Abdul's shop. Taarak then asks a riddle to the men. Will the men work their brains to answer the question? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 351 - Sodhi Is Excited About The Cricket Match
shortDesc: Sodhi gets his dhol fixed to take it along with him to the cricket match. When Taarak informs him about the rules, he doesn't get disappointed. Later Jethalal calls his friend for tickets. Will he get the tickets?
